<descript>
<abstract>Antigua and Barbuda, 1980 is a scanned map of the Caribbean country Antigua and Barbuda at a scale of 1:100,000. The map is comprised with two sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
</descript>
